summary: Solo - A Star Wars Story 2018 (Disney/Lucasfilm) Concepts for the Kessel tunnel. An early idea had an array of beacons that...
caption:
Solo - A Star Wars Story 2018 (Disney/Lucasfilm)

Concepts for the Kessel tunnel. An early idea had an array of beacons that would hold the tunnel open within the cloud. I imagined an effect much like lasers cutting through smoke. Ultimately they went with a more organic design like the bottom frame.


Brett Northcutt

blog.name: siennahasthots
blog.title: Sk
blog.description:
I have thoughts about Star Wars

And other stuff

But mostly Star Wars

body:
Lost Stars

I’m super late to the party when it comes to Claudia Gray’s “Lost Stars”, but damn. That was an entertaining book. Now I have to go back and listen to Bloodline (thanks Audible) again so I can get the timeline worked out… but should I read Leia Princess of Alderaan first?!

My love of Star Wars is ever expanding. Getting into that EU.

title: LEGO do Sandcrawler do Star Wars tem 1.239 peças
body:
LEGO do Sandcrawler do Star Wars tem 1.239 peças

A LEGO lançou recentemente um set de LEGO do Sandcrawler, aquele veículo gigante do Star Wars que caminha no deserto carregando artigos comerciais para venda. Entre esses artigos, claro, estavam C3PO e R2D2.

Este set em questão vem com 1.239 peças e é vendido nos EUA por um valor de US$ 139. Que pena que LEGO é tão caro, não é mesmo?

Ao menos, para matar um pouco da vontade de colocar as mãos em…
